          "settings": {
            "show_badge": false,
            "info_text": "Up to 25% discount applied automatically at checkout. Depends on the bundle – check details here.",
            "info_text_individual": "Up to 25% off on custom orders! Depends on the selected set – check details here.",
            "info_html": "<h2>How does the discount work?</h2> <p>The discount is applied automatically at checkout, but it only applies to bundles starting from 60€ and up.</p> <h3>Discount table:</h3> <table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"10\" cellspacing=\"0\"> <thead> <tr> <th>Order value</th> <th>Bundle type</th> <th>Discount</th> </tr> </thead> <tbody> <tr> <td>from 60€ to 219€</td> <td> – EVAMATS without edges: FRONT, FRONT+REAR, FRONT+REAR+TRUNK<br> – EVAMATS 3D with edges: FRONT </td> <td>-20%</td> </tr> <tr> <td>from 220€ <br>\nand up</td> <td> – EVAMATS 3D with edges: FRONT+REAR, FRONT+REAR+TRUNK<br> – Sets for VANS, BUSES, MINIVANS </td> <td>-25%</td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <h3>Examples:</h3> <ul> <li>Without edges FRONT+REAR+TRUNK (141.74 €) → discount <strong>-20%</strong>\n</li> <li>With edges FRONT+REAR (225.33 €) → discount <strong>-25%</strong>\n</li> </ul> <p><strong>You don't need to do anything – the discount will appear automatically in your cart!</strong></p>",
            "info_html_individual": "<h2>How does the discount work?</h2>\n<p>The discount is applied automatically when placing a custom order, but it only applies to orders starting from €44 and above.</p>\n\n<h3>Discount table:</h3>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"10\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n   <thead>\n      <tr>\n         <th>Order value</th>\n         <th>Bundle type</th>\n         <th>Discount</th>\n      </tr>\n   </thead>\n   <tbody>\n      <tr>\n         <td>from €44 to €219</td>\n         <td>\n         – EVAMATS custom sets without edges: FRONT, FRONT+REAR, FRONT+REAR+TRUNK<br>\n         – EVAMATS 3D custom sets with edges: FRONT\n         </td>\n         <td>-20%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n         <td>from €220 and up</td>\n         <td>\n         – EVAMATS 3D custom sets with edges: FRONT+REAR, FRONT+REAR+TRUNK<br>\n         – Custom sets for VANS, BUSES, MINIVANS\n         </td>\n         <td>-25%</td>\n      </tr>\n   </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h3>Examples:</h3>\n<ul>\n   <li>Custom set without edges FRONT+REAR+TRUNK (€141.74) → discount <strong>-20%</strong>\n</li>\n   <li>Custom set with edges FRONT+REAR (€225.33) → discount <strong>-25%</strong>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>The discount is automatically applied after placing a custom mat order.<br></strong> After submitting your order, our consultant will contact you to confirm the details, provide the final price, and clarify any questions regarding the discount.</p>",
            "individual_welcome_html": "<p><strong>How does an individual order work?</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Configure your set: enter your vehicle details, choose colours and add-ons.</li>\n<li>Pay a deposit: you only pay a small deposit upfront (plus any add-ons in full).</li>\n<li>Confirm details: our consultant will call you to confirm and send the order to production.</li>\n<li>Pay the balance: settle the remainder by bank transfer in advance or on delivery.</li>\n</ol>",
            "auto_open_individual_welcome_popup": true
          }
        },
