        "enable_video_looping": false,
        "trunk_message": "<p>Note – trunk mat:</p><p>Up to 140x240 cm – from one part ✅</p><p>Up to 150x250 cm – from two parts ✅</p><p>Above 280 cm in length – we do not make ❌</p><p>ℹ️ In case of doubt, please contact the sales department.</p>",
        "trunk_message_5_7_os": "<p><strong>Note – trunk mat:</strong></p><p>The trunk has no raised edges – this applies to 3D mats with edges.<br/><br/>In this vehicle model the trunk floor is flat and has no factory side edges. 3D mats with edges will fit the floor but will not create additional raised edges in the trunk.<br/><br/></p>",
