    "product_tabs_646JeH": {
      "type": "product_tabs",
      "blocks": {
        "tab_DcjwUJ": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Description",
            "id": "description",
            "html": "<p><strong>Original EVAMATS Car Mats — Modern Interior Protection</strong></p>\n<p>Our EVA car mats represent a new generation of automotive accessories — lightweight, durable, and water-resistant. Thanks to their unique cellular structure, they trap dirt (mud, sand, water) deep within the material, keeping the surface around them dry and clean.</p>\n<p>Each set is custom-made for a specific car model, precisely tailored to the shape of the floor. You can choose the color, cell pattern, and edging to perfectly match your car’s interior.</p>\n<p><strong>What makes our car mats stand out?</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>💧 100% waterproof — no leaks</li>\n  <li>🧼 Easy to clean — simply shake out or rinse</li>\n  <li>♻️ Safe for health and the environment — toxin-free and recyclable</li>\n  <li>🧩 Customizable — 17 colors, 2 patterns, 14 edging options</li>\n  <li>🚗 Fits 95% of the floor surface</li>\n  <li>❄️ Suitable for all seasons: from -50°C to +50°C</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Enhance the comfort and appearance of your car’s interior with mats that truly make a difference.</p>\n<p><strong>Shop with Confidence</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Expert advice — we’ll help you choose the right set</li>\n  <li>Security — encrypted payments, trusted couriers</li>\n  <li>🇵🇱 Made in Poland — local production, fast delivery</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Trust proven EVA technology and join drivers who value cleanliness, comfort, and style.</p>\n<p>If you’re looking for a durable and practical solution for your car, these mats will exceed your expectations.</p>"
          }
        },
        "tab_RqeNAL": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Specs",
            "id": "tech",
            "html": "<p><strong>🔧 Technical Specifications</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n<strong>Material:</strong> High-quality EVA foam (Ethylene Vinyl Acetate)</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Mat thickness:</strong> Approx. 10 mm — ideal balance between flexibility and durability</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Cell structure:</strong> Diamond (7 mm) / Honeycomb (8 mm) — choose during purchase</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Set weight:</strong> From 1.2 to 2.5 kg (depending on the version)</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Number of pieces:</strong> 2–6 pieces (full set: front + rear + optional trunk)</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Floor coverage:</strong> Up to 95% of the car’s floor surface</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Seasonality:</strong> All-season — resistant to temperatures from -50°C to +50°C</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Water resistance:</strong> 100% — does not absorb liquids, no staining</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Fastening:</strong> Plastic stoppers (original) / Velcro strips — compatible with factory mounting points</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Edging (trim):</strong> 14 color variants to choose from</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Additional options:</strong> Reinforced heel pads</li>\n</ul>"
          }
        },
        "tab_hiraMx": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Delivery and payments",
            "id": "delivery",
            "html": "<p><strong>📦 Delivery and Payment</strong></p>\n\n<p>All EVA mats are made to order from scratch, with attention to detail and a perfect fit for your specific car model.</p>\n\n<p style=\"border:1px solid #ef022d; padding:10px; border-radius:8px;\">💡 The current standard order processing time is 14 business days.</p>\n\n<p>Choose the production speed of your order</p>\n\n<p>Each set of mats is made individually, so you can decide how quickly your order enters production.</p>\n\n<p>Available production options:</p>\n\n<p>🟢 Standard - 14 business days<br>\nProcessed in the standard production queue.</p>\n\n<p>🟠 Express - 7 business days<br>\nHigher priority in the production queue.</p>\n\n<p>Once production is completed, the mats are immediately prepared for shipment.</p>\n\n<p>You can choose the priority production option on the “Delivery and Payment” page when selecting the delivery method. The Express service is available at an additional cost.</p>\n\n<p>🚗 We do our best to process orders as quickly as possible. However, during periods of increased order volume, such as seasonal peaks, promotions, or holidays, processing times may be extended.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Delivery methods:</strong></p>\n\n<div class=\"product_tabs__containers_item_block\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0734/7988/1010/files/Frame_427319187.svg?v=1754576315\" alt=\"InPost\"> \n  <ul>\n    <li>InPost Courier (online payment or cash on delivery)</li>\n    <li>InPost Parcel Locker (online payment only)</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"product_tabs__containers_item_block\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0734/7988/1010/files/dpd.svg?v=1754574037\" alt=\"DPD\"> \n  <ul>\n    <li>DPD Courier (online payment or cash on delivery)</li>\n    <li>DPD Pickup Point (online payment only)</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"product_tabs__containers_item_block\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0790/9218/7414/files/GLS_Logo_2021_svg.svg?v=1774966899\" alt=\"GLS\"> \n  <ul>\n    <li>GLS Courier (online payment or cash on delivery)</li>\n    <li>GLS Parcel Shop (online payment only)</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>\n\n<p><strong>Online payments:</strong></p>\n\n<p>\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0734/7988/1010/files/przelewy24_logo_svg.svg?v=1754575627\" alt=\"Przelewy24\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0734/7988/1010/files/blik_9f0af63c-fe50-41e4-9eed-8eba66188150.svg?v=1754574036\" alt=\"BLIK\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0734/7988/1010/files/PayPo_logo_kolor.svg?v=1754574985\" alt=\"PayPo\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0734/7988/1010/files/visa_f5353cf6-3937-47e8-b0d0-4dffa5d38d04.svg?v=1754574037\" alt=\"Visa\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0734/7988/1010/files/mc_e03f8da5-c6a9-4429-bc4f-800d875497b5.svg?v=1754574036\" alt=\"Mastercard\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0734/7988/1010/files/apay_01efa87d-bab1-4df5-8583-9bd84c0efe6c.svg?v=1754575856\" alt=\"Apple Pay\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0734/7988/1010/files/gpay_763ff9ab-ac05-4efa-ae2a-34b490f1dbc2.svg?v=1754574037\" alt=\"Google Pay\">\n</p>\n\n<p><strong>Safe shopping:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Encrypted payments</li>\n  <li>Reliable logistics</li>\n  <li>Ongoing customer support</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Thank you for choosing a Polish-made product designed with quality and functionality in mind. Driver satisfaction is our top priority.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
